title: ManageDataResult
description:
ManageDataResult is an XDR Union defined as:

```text union ManageDataResult switch (ManageDataResultCode code) { case MANAGE_DATA_SUCCESS: void; case MANAGE_DATA_NOT_SUPPORTED_YET: case MANAGE_DATA_NAME_NOT_FOUND: case MANAGE_DATA_LOW_RESERVE: case MANAGE_DATA_INVALID_NAME: void; }; ```
